LuaBase 1.0

* Concept

 LuaBase aims to make a GUI enviroment for easy programming 
and a full customizable launcher for linux handhelds
and eventually you can develop simple programs on handhelds with only a text editor.

* History

2011-06-16
 Rebuild directory structure and improve system

2011-06-07
 Improved some delay and fixed Keyboard cursor.

2011-06-06
 Developer preview is released.

* LuaBase links with ...
 Lua 
 SDL
 SDL_ttf
 SDL_image
 SDL_mixer
 
 Please see license folder for the details.
 
